1c:["$","p",null,{"children":"UDP drops frames without stalling. A dropped voice frame causes a brief click. The jitter buffer (50–200 ms) on the receiver absorbs burst packet timing. The listening experience on a lossy satellite link is fundamentally better."}]
1d:["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Why not v1?"}]," UDP requires a separate socket, a custom RTP framing implementation, and a jitter buffer — a full additional subsystem. The server relay logic needs to handle both protocols. At one week, we ship WebSocket and document the upgrade path."]}]
